{"id": 1183, "genre": 1001, "title": "当你说“我遭遇了办公室政治”的时候，其实是在说什么？", "description": "好像也没有厚黑系职场小说里的你死我活，那么现实生活中会发生的是什么呢？（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 2640, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170322102553BKZympwIxJck5AEz.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-08-27T17:03:18Z", "options": [{"id": 111375, "content": "太容易把宽容当成软弱，把虚张声势当成强硬", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 157661}, {"id": 111382, "content": "不了解。但是害怕", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 718259}, {"id": 111385, "content": "什么人都有，每个人都跟自己不一样。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1030252}, {"id": 111392, "content": "1、接盘侠\n2、没有一个领导会虚心纳谏，他们只会虚心纳妾。\n3、领导是一种可以违背能量守恒定律的存在。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 691271}, {"id": 111393, "content": "强者自强 弱者闭嘴", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 725485}, {"id": 111298, "content": "不是所有的坏人都是坏人，不是所有的好人都是好人，关键时刻看你的可利用价值程度。", "image": null, "praise_count": 148, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 729310}, {"id": 111364, "content": "被人摆了一道", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 700694}, {"id": 111366, "content": "1.婊永远在\n2.潜规则水太深\n3.升职不等于能力\n4.你行不行，上司一句话而已", "image": null, "praise_count": 104, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 259974}, {"id": 111367, "content": "跟同事一起周五晚上在酒桌上放松时，别发公司的牢骚", "image": null, "praise_count": 44, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 155259}, {"id": 111368, "content": "被實力甩鍋", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 532979}, {"id": 111371, "content": "与业绩无关，与取向有关", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 477196}, {"id": 111372, "content": "同事只是同事，离开办公室后能不联系就不联系，烦人！", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 649741}, {"id": 111377, "content": "前一秒和你嬉笑 下一秒责任全是你", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 735099}, {"id": 111380, "content": "公司说每年固定的promotion都会意外地delay或者cancel?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 687677}, {"id": 111384, "content": "领导再蠢也是领导?", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 735800}, {"id": 111386, "content": "部门之间互相推诿 基层苦成狗也是那点钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 389468}, {"id": 111387, "content": "大呼小叫的蒋健", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 730133}, {"id": 111388, "content": "上层不惜动用大量人力物力来动几个部门集权", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 701249}, {"id": 111396, "content": "能力不够", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 680805}, {"id": 111397, "content": "寻找战斗的兴奋点，找不到不如急流勇退", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 735935}, {"id": 113446, "content": "办公室里总有那么一个两面三刀的bitch", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 747023}, {"id": 111400, "content": "别人在抱怨领导的时候千万不要跟着抱怨。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 648759}, {"id": 111402, "content": "领导永远说的对！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 725146}, {"id": 111406, "content": "真心搞不懂哪来的这么多心机婊&心机boy??太闹心了", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 735994}, {"id": 111408, "content": "遇事时，领导更愿意相信什么活都不干的那位", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 733480}, {"id": 111409, "content": "勾心斗角 不是朋友", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 736015}, {"id": 111410, "content": "影帝多如牛毛  碎嘴遍地开花", "image": null, "praise_count": 28, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 736030}, {"id": 111411, "content": "发个朋友圈 hr就找谈话了哈哈哈哈哈哈哈路菲杰就这样\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 609852}, {"id": 111413, "content": "职场里还会有些中庸之人 审时度势 随机应变 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 199344}, {"id": 111415, "content": "只有永远的利益，没有永远的同事", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 736090}, {"id": 111417, "content": "永远一些人打着关心你的旗号，八卦你的生活", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 736109}, {"id": 111418, "content": "新领导来了，挑拨原有同事之间的关系，巩固自己势力", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 728664}, {"id": 111419, "content": "人和人之间一定会有阶级之分。原因是99%的人都有一个很难克服的本性“懒”。有上进心勤奋的人如果成功了，阶级自然而然就产生了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 666258}, {"id": 111421, "content": "拒绝卷入办公室政治", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 701843}, {"id": 177470, "content": "心态，情商和反应能力很重要", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 965984}, {"id": 111424, "content": "领导爱在你后面逼叨", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 718262}, {"id": 111425, "content": "不如别人会拍马屁？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 736174}, {"id": 111426, "content": "诚邀小说DA字员及掏寳简直人员，每天9O-36O是没有问题的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 704211}, {"id": 111430, "content": "大领导谈话就是给你画饼充饥，习惯就好。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 720999}, {"id": 111434, "content": "并不是踏实做事的人才能生存下来，那些插科打诨溜须拍马的人说不定混的比你还要好。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 338358}, {"id": 111436, "content": "工作两年后，明白了工作这件事情，尽到自己的责任就好，不要拼命，毕竟最后再努力领导开的也只是空头支票。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 626118}, {"id": 111437, "content": "代表想太多了。", "image": "img/option/option/20160828220432ObnVQ8PS36XRBzl5.jpg", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 709604}, {"id": 111441, "content": "用心对待你的工作，你会有回报和收获", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 526809}, {"id": 111953, "content": "  跟领导打好关系，跟同事相处融洽，不爽时闭着嘴CTM。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 740101}, {"id": 111442, "content": "会吵的小孩有糖吃。前提，要么孩爸是**，要么有干爹。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 736297}, {"id": 111443, "content": "被坑了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 736317}, {"id": 111446, "content": "勾心斗角。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 736343}, {"id": 111703, "content": "我要离职了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 152600}, {"id": 111448, "content": "官大一级玩死你", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 114997}, {"id": 111449, "content": "。。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 718057}]}